snippet.title: House of Volunteers
snippet.description:
At House of Volunteers Australia, our the team intends to bring volunteering opportunities closer to the students of Sydney. 
Most of the volunteer sites are capitalize by advertising making them very problematic to navigate and not targeted to students. 
We are dedicated to connecting students and parents with the charities that are actively looking for youth volunteers.
